snippet.title: Project Coreward Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Exoplanet's full release, including act I, II and III and over 10 hours of gameplay will come as Project Coreward, a proper tribute to Starflight. 

I've thought about this game and it's development for over a decade. The work has been completed. The project is finally ready for a release. 

Project Coreward's full release is tentatively scheduled for 11/27/2023 at 1PM EST.
